&ldquo;Thanks for reaching out. We&rsquo;ve reviewed the content, and didn&rsquo;t find a violation of our policies, so no action will be taken at this time,&rdquo; the response reads, according to the lawsuit. <br />
<br />
&ldquo;If you believe there&rsquo;s a potential copyright infringement, please start a new report. If the content is hosted on a third-party website, you&rsquo;ll need to contact that website&rsquo;s support team to report it. Your safety is the most important thing, and if you believe you are in danger, we encourage you to contact your local authorities.&rdquo;

